00:42:04,840 --> 00:42:06,730
Zobuď sa, Ji Hyeon.

552
00:42:08,040 --> 00:42:09,150
Ji Hyeon.

553
00:42:09,910 --> 00:42:12,130
Odpovedz mi, ak si hore.

554
00:42:12,780 --> 00:42:13,790
Hej!

555
00:42:15,980 --> 00:42:17,160
Hej, si v poriadku?

556
00:42:17,750 --> 00:42:18,860
Seol Ji Hyeon!

557
00:42:34,670 --> 00:42:36,590
Hej, Ji Hyeon.

558
00:42:36,710 --> 00:42:39,500
Ji Hyeon, hej!

559
00:42:39,810 --> 00:42:42,130
Hej, preber sa!

560
00:42:59,360 --> 00:43:01,600
Je podvyživená a mierne dehydrovaná.

561
00:43:01,600 --> 00:43:03,820
Bude jej lepšie,
keď si oddýchne a niečo zje.

562
00:43:27,320 --> 00:43:30,390
Nemôžeš byť chorá, Ji Hyeon.

563
00:43:40,170 --> 00:43:41,860
To všetko kvôli mne...

564
00:43:45,870 --> 00:43:46,990
Všetko...

565
00:44:23,580 --> 00:44:26,070
Myslíš si,
že dokážeš zmeniť svet?

566
00:44:56,100 --> 00:45:01,100
<i>Titulky preložilo Škaredé Káčatko</i>

567
00:45:37,020 --> 00:45:38,650
2, 3,

568
00:45:38,650 --> 00:45:41,890
- 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10.
- Bože.

569
